First Petroleum and Pipeline Inc

OTC BB: mli9.67


Date: Wedday, April 17-21, 2006
Current Price: 0.0033
Short Term Target: 0.05
Long Term Target: 0.20
Status: Very 55.sk1  Buy


First Petroleum is an independent gas and oil exploration and
development company. The main company goal is to apply advanced
technologies to systematically explore and develop its oil and natural
gas opportunities within its Colorado, New Mexico, and Wyoming
properties. First Petroleum focuses its activities where expertise can
be used to efficiently to maximize returns on invested capital by
reducing risk enhancing its ability to economically grow reserves and
production volumes. 

First Petroleum has recently secured the rights to eleven Federal Oil
and Gas Leases. First Petroleum will now focus on potential drill
programs and development of the most promising leasing properties in
its portfolio. First Petroleum believes that future developments in
their target regions could give the resources necessary to build the
dedicated management team and to pursue further strategic acquisitions
of proven or semi-proven exploration targets. The company will remained
focused on this strategy.
